Package: Sequgio
Type: Package
Title: Isoform expression estimation based on RNA-seq data
Version: 0.6.0
Date: 2014-06-25
Author: Suo Chen <chen.suo@ki.se>
Maintainer: Stefano Calza <stefano.calza@ki.se>
Description: This package provides an algorithm to estimate isoforms expression from RNA-seq data based on a model that 
	     doesn't assume uniform distribution of count within transcripts.
	     Accessories function to import BAM data are also provided
License: Artistic-2.0
LazyLoad: yes
Depends: R(> 3.1.0)
Imports: AnnotationDbi, Rcpp(>= 0.11.1), RcppArmadillo(>= 0.4.100.2.1), nnls(>= 1.4),
         GenomicAlignments(>= 0.99.32), bigmemory(>= 4.4.6), Rsamtools(>= 1.15.37),
	 BiocParallel(>= 0.5.18), GenomicRanges(>= 1.15.41), BH(>= 1.54.0-2)
Suggests: RNAseqData.HNRNPC.bam.chr14, TxDb.Hsapiens.UCSC.hg19.knownGene
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo, bigmemory, BH, IRanges, S4Vectors
